693    private function partitionCollections($list, $size, $tsumegoStatusMap)
694    {
695        $newList = [];
696        $listCount = count($list);
697        for ($i = 0; $i < $listCount; $i++)
698        {
699            $amountTags = $list[$i]['amount'];
700            $amountCounter = 0;
701            $amountFrom = 0;
702            $amountTo = $size - 1;
703            while ($amountTags > $size)
704            {
705                $newList = $this->partitionCollection($newList, $list[$i], $size, $tsumegoStatusMap, $amountFrom, $amountTo + 1, $amountCounter, true);
706                $amountTags -= $size;
707                $amountCounter++;
708                $amountFrom += $size;
709                $amountTo += $size;
710            }
711            $amountTo = $amountFrom + $amountTags;
712            $newList = $this->partitionCollection($newList, $list[$i], $amountTags, $tsumegoStatusMap, $amountFrom, $amountTo, $amountCounter, false);
713        }
714
715        return $newList;
716    }
717
718    private function partitionCollection($newList, $list, $size, $tsumegoStatusMap, $from, $to, $amountCounter, $inLoop)
719    {
720        $tl = [];
721        $tl['id'] = $list['id'];
722        $colorValue = 1;
723        if (!$inLoop && $amountCounter == 0)
724            $tl['partition'] = -1;
725        else
726        {
727            $tl['partition'] = $amountCounter;
728            $step = 1.5;
729            $colorValue = 1 - ($amountCounter * 0.1 * $step);
730        }
731        $tl['name'] = $list['name'];
732        $tl['amount'] = $size;
733        $tl['color'] = str_replace('[o]', (string) $colorValue, $list['color']);
734        if (isset($list['premium']))
735            $tl['premium'] = $list['premium'];
736        else
737            $tl['premium'] = 0;
738        $currentIds = [];
739        for ($i = $from; $i < $to; $i++)
740            array_push($currentIds, $list['currentIds'][$i]);
741        $difficultyAndSolved = $this->getDifficultyAndSolved($currentIds, $tsumegoStatusMap);
742        $tl['difficulty'] = $difficultyAndSolved['difficulty'];
743        $tl['solved_percent'] = $difficultyAndSolved['solved'];
744        array_push($newList, $tl);
745
746        return $newList;
747    }

749    private function getDifficultyAndSolved($currentTagIds, $tsumegoStatusMap)
750    {
751        $tagTsumegoDifficulty = $this->Tsumego->find('all', ['conditions' => ['id' => $currentTagIds]]);
752        if (!$tagTsumegoDifficulty)
753            $tagTsumegoDifficulty = [];
754        $tagDifficultyResult = 0;
755        $statusCounter = 0;
756        $tagTsumegoDifficultyCount2 = count($tagTsumegoDifficulty);
757        for ($j = 0; $j < $tagTsumegoDifficultyCount2; $j++)
758        {
759            $tagDifficultyResult += $tagTsumegoDifficulty[$j]['Tsumego']['rating'];
760            if (isset($tsumegoStatusMap[$tagTsumegoDifficulty[$j]['Tsumego']['id']]))
761                if ($tsumegoStatusMap[$tagTsumegoDifficulty[$j]['Tsumego']['id']] == 'S' || $tsumegoStatusMap[$tagTsumegoDifficulty[$j]['Tsumego']['id']] == 'W' || $tsumegoStatusMap[$tagTsumegoDifficulty[$j]['Tsumego']['id']] == 'C')
762                    $statusCounter++;
763        }
764        if (count($tagTsumegoDifficulty) > 0)
765            $tagDifficultyResult = $tagDifficultyResult / count($tagTsumegoDifficulty);
766        else
767            $tagDifficultyResult = 0;
768        $tagDifficultyResult = Rating::getReadableRankFromRating($tagDifficultyResult);
769        $return = [];
770        $return['difficulty'] = $tagDifficultyResult;
771        if (count($currentTagIds) > 0)
772            $return['solved'] = round($statusCounter / count($currentTagIds) * 100, 2);
773        else
774            $return['solved'] = 0;
775
776        return $return;
777    }

779    /**
780     * Gets the first unsolved set connection ID from a collection of tsumego buttons.
781     * Falls back to the first button if all are solved.
782     *
783     * @param TsumegoButtons $tsumegoButtons Iterator of TsumegoButton objects
784     * @return int|null The setConnectionID of the first unsolved button, or first button if all solved, or null if empty
785     */
786    private function getFirstUnsolvedSetConnectionId($tsumegoButtons)
787    {
788        if (empty($tsumegoButtons))
789            return null;
790        if ($firstUnsolvedButton = array_find((array) $tsumegoButtons, function ($tsumegoButton) {
791            return !TsumegoUtil::isSolvedStatus($tsumegoButton->status);
792        }))
793            return $firstUnsolvedButton->setConnectionID;
794        if ($firstRecentlyUnsolved = array_find((array) $tsumegoButtons, function ($tsumegoButton) {
795            return !TsumegoUtil::isRecentlySolved($tsumegoButton->status);
796        }))
797            return $firstRecentlyUnsolved->setConnectionID;
798        return $tsumegoButtons[0]->setConnectionID;
799    }

849    private function decodeQueryType($input)
850    {
851        if (is_numeric($input))
852            return 'topics';
853        if ($input == 'favorites')
854            return 'favorites';
855        try
856        {
857            Rating::getRankFromReadableRank($input);
858            return 'difficulty';
859        }
860        catch (Exception $e)
861        {
862            return 'tags';
863        }
864    }
